content: This role has the operation rights of all functions of the application enablement module, data set management rights of the data enablement module, model service rights of the model enablement module, and service access rights of the settings.
该角色拥有应用使能模块所有功能的操作权限，拥有数据使能模块数据集管理的操作权限，拥有模型使能模块模型服务的操作权限，拥有设置中服务接入的操作权限。
This role has only the app dialog operation permission for App Enablement AppGallery.
该角色仅拥有应用使能应用市场的应用对话操作权限。
This role has full operational permissions for the data enablement module, model enablement module, and application enablement module, as well as permissions to manage service access in the settings.
该角色拥有数据使能模块，模型使能模块，应用使能模块的全部操作权限，拥有设置中服务接入的操作权限。
